{"title":"再許一個转山转水转佛塔的開始","slug":"tibet","date":"2019-01-01T15:38:28.000Z","updated":"2024-04-18T13:18:11.119Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/tibet.json","excerpt":"2018年的最后一个工作日，没有加班，在 push 完今年最后一个 commit 后，就回屋收拾东西，纠结了半天，还是背上了大法，也把胶片机塞进了行李箱，开始期待 2018 会有怎样一个 ending。","covers":["https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/1546007957306.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/P81230-103254.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/1546147354106.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/1546147441743.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/1546147485318.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-23.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-19.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-20.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-21.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-22.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-24.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-25.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-26.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-27.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-29.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-30.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-31.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-32.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibet-33.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/tibet/Tibe